```CSS CSS
/* Keyword value */
grid-column-end: auto;

/* <custom-ident> values */
grid-row-start: somegridarea;

/* span + <integer> + <custom-ident> values */
grid-row-start: span 3;

/* Global values */
grid-row-start: inherit;
grid-row-start: initial;
grid-row-start: unset;
```

